SUMMARY:Sunday Funday Blues Jam
DESCRIPTION:The Sunday Funday Blues Jam is THE hottest blues jam in the North Bay!\nA fun night for blues fans and the players are having a blast! \nWe are all about the blues and we love to Honor the greats that came before us as well as provide a stage for players you don’t have a place to play on Sunday nights. \nWe love dancers too!! You have no idea what you do for a musician when you just show up. So whether you’re a dancer singer player or just love the blues\, we’ve got a place saved you. \nThis is a player’s jam come ready.
