SUMMARY:The North Bay Get Down (Free Monthly Funk Jam)
DESCRIPTION:THE BEST MONDAY NIGHT IN THE NORTH BAY! 3rd Monday Each Month. This is a live monthly funk jam and dance party for musicians and music lovers of all kinds! Each month features a DJ\, then a rotating “House Band” of the top musicians\, followed by a curated/open jam – all music is improvised on the spot for a community funk dance party. Great live music\, dancing\, drinks\, and community vibes. Hosted by Ethan Schiff! \n6:30pm: Doors + Live DJ\n7:15 (ish): House Band Jam\n8-10pm: Curated/Open Jam \n*3rd Monday Every Month\n*Follow @NorthBayGetDown on Instagram for real-time updates
