SUMMARY:VINYL TAP – Eagles\, Stones\, Doobies (you get the idea)
DESCRIPTION:Because who doesn’t like classic rock?! OK\, here’s the deal. Unless you’ve been living under a rock for the past several decades\, and you know who you are\, you will know all of the songs on the set list. We’ll nail the iconic instrumental and vocal parts and grooves so you won’t want to miss the opportunity to come out and dance\, sing\, carry on – whatever it is that you do to live music. And heck\, there’s no cover so what’s the holdup?
