SUMMARY:FLAMENCO! LIVE! Saturday\, May 9\, 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an intoxicating evening of fiery flamenco performances when FLAMENCO! LIVE! sets the stage on fire with the fury and passion of Spain’s legendary Gypsies (Roma) in the intimate atmosphere of THE BIG EASY. Stirring dances\, blazing guitars\, and soulful singing will transport you to another place and time. FEEL the HEAT… \nFLAMENCO!\nLIVE! \n2 Flamenco Dancers\nSinger\nand Guitarist \nShowtime: 6 pm\nDoors: 5 pm\n$25\nPay at the Door\nCash or Card \nFlamenco dancers\, guitarists and singers set the stage on Fire! \nat\nThe Big Easy\nClub and Restaurant\n128 American Alley\nPetaluma USA\n*****************************************\nEvery other Month Flamenco Shows!\nThe 2nd Saturday of the Month.\nAlways different Artists.\nAlways a different Show. \nFull bar and Dinner menu with delicious food are available\, not included in entrance fee. \nArrive early\, get a good table and enjoy the food!\nLine forms at 4:45 pm \n*Reservations for parties of 5 or more only:\n(707) 774- 9072 \nwww.flamencolive.weebly.com
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/flamenco-live-saturday-may-9-2026/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/FLAMENCO-LIVE-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
